command: Hello! I am glad you were able to make it.
You are here to fight the Giants, right?
Good! You are Peter, right? High King of Narnia?

You know, the Giants that are terrorizing the entire country of the North?
I sent for help a week ago to Narnia. You are Peter, right?

Good! I didn't send much information before, so here is what happened:
The Giants used to be freindly up here, but one day, things changed.

They did not come out of their caves one day. After a while, they still 
did not come out. One day, we were starting to get worried, so we
sent someone into their caves. He did not come out again.

A while later, we recieved a threat from them. We did not know where 
it came from, but it did say that they were going to take over, and they
wanted to be in control. We could either let them, or fight them.
We had one month to make a decision. That was 2 weeks ago.

I'm asking if you would like to help us beat them, and uncover what 
is happening. What do you say? I'll help too!

WHAT? No... please please please please please please please please
please please please please pleeease let me go with you!!!
I will be a big help! Come on, you got to let me come with you!
THANK YOU SO SO SO MUCH!!

[i][b]Grrr...[/b][/i] How about you fight me? If you win, you can
go alone!
HAHA! You forfit! That counts as a win for me!
YES! LET'S GOO! I BEAT YOU!

I'm on your team now! Oh yeah, I also refilled your health. Also, I have
to admit, I kind of cheated.... but never mind. Just keep in mind I'm
not actually that powerfull.
Let's go out that blue-green tunnel, up ahead
